    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 16 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 4 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 16</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You change into a more beast-like form, becoming half predator, half man. You gain a claw and bite attack, dealing damage as though an animal of your size category, and gain a +4 competence bonus to Intimidate checks. In addition, you can move up to three times your speed when charging. If you fall unconscious, the technique ends.</p>\n\n\n\n",
